                <fr:title text="Forester 5.0 [TBA] › simplifications to the source language › removal of imports within subtrees"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/OYOT.xml" title="Forester 5.0 [TBA] › simplifications to the source language" addr="forest://forester/OYOT" type="local"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/jms-011P.xml" title="Forester 5.0 [TBA]" addr="forest://forester/jms-011P" type="local">Forester 5.0 [TBA]</fr:link> › simplifications to the source language</fr:link> › removal of imports within subtrees</fr:title>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>It is no longer permitted to have an <html:code><![CDATA[\import]]></html:code> declaration within a subtree: these can occur only at the top level of a file and therefore have file-level scope.</html:p>
